  <history>Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase. The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. 2 gap errors were fixed. One was between the borders of Admin1 units "Racha-Lechkhumi and Kvemo Svaneti" and "Provisional Administration". The other was between the borders of Admin3 units "Khelvachauri" and "Keda".</history>
